    <h1>Autoverse Agent</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">Comprehensive Final Project Report & Feature Specification</div>

    <h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>
    <p>
        <strong>Autoverse Agent</strong> is a full-stack, zero-configuration Artificial Intelligence platform designed to democratize AI customer service. It provides website owners with a drop-in chat widget that autonomously reads, understands, and serves the content of their website to visitors. By combining web scraping, Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG), and advanced prompt engineering via the Groq API, Autoverse delivers a highly accurate, multi-lingual, and context-aware virtual assistant capable of acting as both an informational guide and an automated e-commerce sales agent.
    </p>

    <h2>2. System Architecture</h2>
    <p>
        Autoverse Agent is engineered on a modern, production-grade microservices architecture that strictly decouples client-side execution, core API routing, database persistence, and administrative controls. By splitting these responsibilities, the application secures high availability, limits memory footprint, guarantees sub-second latency, and simplifies continuous integration and multi-platform deployments (Railway, Vercel, and NPM).
    </p>

